        <Meaning id="088b12c1-1876-4102-a7a2-016c756f859e" type="Verb">
          <Vi>Quay quỹ đạo; bay quỹ đạo</Vi>
          <En>To move in a curved path around a celestial body or object; to circle around something.</En>
          <Example>The satellite will orbit Earth for five years before deorbiting.</Example>
